author.name: Woo Commerce 2022
author.details: WooCommerce comes packaged with archive pages and loops that make the WooCommerce product description display awesome. Yet here and there you may need to show more data on your main shop and other archive pages. This tutorial demonstrates how to show a WooCommerce short description of products to archive pages and display it below the title of the product. You can also add a minimum shipping requirement rule on products.
